## 🌐 WHAT CRM MANAGES (Full Control)

### 1. "GT Website" Management (New Grouping)
The CRM sidebar will have a dedicated section for "GT Websites" with three sub-sections/buttons to manage each website independently:

**A. GT Main Company**
- Global News & Press Releases
- Global Staff/Board Profiles
- Investor Relations / General Info

**B. GT Group Nexus Digital**
- Nexus Services
- Nexus Portfolio / Case Studies
- B2B / B2C Client Testimonials
- Nexus Contact Forms / Inquiries

**C. GT Group Study Abroad**
- Study Destinations
- Partner Universities
- Scholarships
- Public Events
- Academic Programs
- Student Testimonials

