## ✨ TRANSPARENT GLASS UI DESIGN SPEC

### Glassmorphism Token Standard (v2.0)
```css
/* Premium Glass Card */
background: linear-gradient(135deg,
  rgba(239,183,72,0.06) 0%,
  rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 100%);
backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
border: 1px solid rgba(239,183,72,0.15);
box-shadow:
  0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
  inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
```

### Theme Logic
- **Default:** Automatically detects user's system preferences (`prefers-color-scheme`).
- **Dark Mode:** Background `#0F1110`, Surface `#161918`, Official Gold accents.
- **Light Mode:** Background `#F7F3EC`, Surface `#FFFFFF`, Gold gradients.

